# The Databricks-App export template ships real frontend source dirs named
# `lib/` (shadcn utils, markdown renderer, deck themes) — both frontend/src/lib/
# AND the vendored renderer's frontend/src/a2ui/lib/. These are NOT Python venv
# libs — keep them tracked despite the `lib/` rule above, else exports break on a
# fresh clone (the files exist locally but never get committed, and the vendored
# a2ui/components.tsx imports from a2ui/lib/deckThemes.ts that isn't there).
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/lib/
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/lib/**
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/a2ui/lib/
!src/engines/crewai/exporters/templates/databricks_app/frontend/src/a2ui/lib/**
parts/
sdist/
var/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

